2:T70f,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Serpstat better than Surfer SEO?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Serpstat scores 7.0 overall while Surfer SEO scores 8.0. Serpstat is best for SMBs and in-house SEOs, while Surfer SEO excels for content writers and SEO specialists."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Serpstat or Surfer SEO?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Serpstat starts at $69/mo and Surfer SEO starts at $99/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Serpstat to Surfer SEO?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Serpstat and Surfer SEO support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Serpstat vs Surfer SEO?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Serpstat holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10. Surfer SEO has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Serpstat for good value for comprehensive features and Surfer SEO for best-in-class content optimization scoring."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Serpstat or Surfer SEO?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Surfer SEO for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Serpstat remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize good value for comprehensive features. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"clas