c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Serpstat and Surfer SEO share a solid foundation of core features including Keyword Research, Site Audit, Content Optimization, Competitor Analysis. Where Serpstat pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Rank Tracking and Backlink Analysis, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Surfer SEO uniquely offers Ai Writing, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Serpstat holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Surfer SEO scores 8/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Serpstat offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $69/mo, compared to Surfer SEO's starting price of $99/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
